## Article Entity

An article represents a blog post with the following properties:
- **id**: Unique identifier (UUID)
- **title**: The article headline
- **slug**: URL-friendly identifier derived from title
- **content**: Full article content in Markdown format
- **excerpt**: Short summary (max 200 characters)
- **author**: Author name or ID
- **category**: Single category classification
- **tags**: Array of topic tags
- **status**: One of 'draft', 'published', or 'archived'
- **publishedAt**: ISO date when published (null if draft)
- **createdAt/updatedAt**: Timestamps
